SELECT USERNAME AS Name, USER_ID AS ID, CREATED AS CreateDate FROM SYS.ALL_USERS WHERE (USERNAME=:NAME or CAST (:NAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) ORDER BY USERNAME

SELECT OWNER, OBJECT_NAME AS TABLE_NAME, DECODE(OWNER, 'SYS', 'System', 'SYSTEM', 'System', 'SYSMAN', 'System','CTXSYS', 'System','MDSYS', 'System','OLAPSYS', 'System', 'ORDSYS', 'System','OUTLN', 'System', 'WKSYS', 'System','WMSYS', 'System','XDB', 'System','ORDPLUGINS', 'System', 'TTREP', 'System', 'GRID', 'System', 'User') AS Type FROM SYS.ALL_OBJECTS WHERE (OWNER=:OWNER or CAST (:OWNER AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) AND (OBJECT_NAME = :TABLENAME or CAST (:TABLENAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) is NULL) AND OBJECT_TYPE = 'TABLE' ORDER BY OWNER, OBJECT_NAME

SELECT RTRIM (TABLES.TBLOWNER) AS OWNER, RTRIM (TABLES.TBLNAME) AS TABLE_NAME, RTRIM (COLUMNS.COLNAME) AS COLUMN_NAME, COLNUM AS ID, CASE WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 1 THEN 'TT_SMALLINT' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 2 THEN 'TT_INTEGER' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 3 THEN 'BINARY_FLOAT' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 4 THEN 'BINARY_DOUBLE' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 5 THEN 'TT_CHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 6 THEN 'TT_VARCHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 7 THEN 'BINARY' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 8 THEN 'VARBINARY' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 11 THEN 'TT_DECIMAL' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 12 THEN 'TT_NCHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 13 THEN 'TT_NVARCHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 14 THEN 'TT_DATE' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 15 THEN 'TIME' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 16 THEN 'TT_TIMESTAMP' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 20 THEN 'TT_TINYINT' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 21 THEN 'TT_BIGINT' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 22 THEN 'TT_VARCHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 23 THEN 'VARBINARY' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 24 THEN 'TT_NVARCHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 25 AND COLUMNS.SYS10 = 128 AND COLUMNS.TYPE_ATTR != 0 THEN 'FLOAT' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 25 THEN 'NUMBER' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 26 THEN 'CHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 27 THEN 'VARCHAR2' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 28 THEN 'NCHAR' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 29 THEN 'NVARCHAR2' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 30 THEN 'DATE' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 31 THEN 'TIMESTAMP (' || TO_CHAR (COLUMNS.SYS10) || ')' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 32 THEN 'VARCHAR2' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 33 THEN 'NVARCHAR2' WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE = 34 THEN 'ROWID' END AS DATATYPE, COLLEN AS LENGTH, CASE WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE IN (5,6,22,26,27,32,12,13,24,28,29,33) THEN NULL WHEN COLUMNS.SYS10 = 128 AND COLUMNS.TYPE_ATTR != 0 THEN COLUMNS.TYPE_ATTR WHEN COLUMNS.SYS10 = 128 OR COLUMNS.COLTYPE IN (14,15,16,30,31) THEN NULL ELSE COLUMNS.SYS9 END AS PRECISION, CASE WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE IN (5,6,22,26,27,32,12,13,24,28,29,33) THEN NULL WHEN COLUMNS.SYS10 = 128 THEN NULL ELSE COLUMNS.SYS10 END AS SCALE, CASE WHEN COLUMNS.COLOPTIONS IN (0x00,0x01,0x02) THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END AS NULLABLE, CHAR_USED, CASE WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE IN (5,6,22,26,27,32) THEN COLLEN WHEN COLUMNS.COLTYPE IN (12,13,24,28,29,33) THEN COLLEN / 2 ELSE 0 END AS LENGTHINCHARS FROM SYS.TABLES, SYS.COLUMNS WHERE TABLES.TBLID = COLUMNS.ID AND (TABLES.TBLOWNER = :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS TT_VARCHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (TABLES.TBLNAME = :TABLENAME OR CAST (:TABLENAME AS TT_VARCHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (COLUMNS.COLNAME = :COLUMNNAME OR CAST (:COLUMNNAME AS TT_VARCHAR (31)) IS NULL) ORDER BY TABLES.TBLOWNER, TABLES.TBLNAME, COLUMNS.COLNUM

SELECT RTRIM (OWNER) AS OWNER, RTRIM (NAME) AS VIEW_NAME, LENGTH (SQL) AS TEXT_LENGTH, SQL AS TEXT, CAST (NULL AS NUMBER) AS TYPE_TEXT_LENGTH, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (4000)) AS TYPE_TEXT, CAST (NULL AS NUMBER) AS OID_TEXT_LENGTH, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (4000)) AS OID_TEXT, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS VIEW_TYPE_OWNER, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS VIEW_TYPE, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS SUPERVIEW_NAME, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (1)) AS EDITIONING_VIEW, 'Y' AS READ_ONLY FROM SYS.VIEWS WHERE (OWNER = :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) AND (NAME = :VIEWNAME OR CAST (:VIEWNAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL)
SELECT * FROM SYS.ALL_SYNONYMS WHERE (OWNER = :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) AND (SYNONYM_NAME = :SYNONYMNAME OR CAST (:SYNONYMNAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL)

SELECT RTRIM (OWNER) AS SEQUENCE_OWNER, RTRIM (NAME) AS SEQUENCE_NAME, MINVAL AS MIN_VALUE, MAXVAL AS MAX_VALUE, INCREMENT AS INCREMENT_BY, CASE CYCLE WHEN 0x00 THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END AS CYCLE_FLAG, NULL AS ORDER_FLAG, CACHESIZE AS CACHE_SIZE, LASTNUMBER AS LAST_NUMBER FROM SYS.SEQUENCES WHERE (OWNER = :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS TT_CHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (NAME = :SEQUENCENAME OR CAST (:SEQUENCENAME AS TT_CHAR (31)) IS NULL)

TABLE_TYPE, CASE INDEXES.ISUNIQUE WHEN 0x00 THEN 'NONUNIQUE' ELSE 'UNIQUE' END AS UNIQUENESS, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (8)) AS COMPRESSION, CAST (NULL AS NUMBER) AS PREFIX_LENGTH, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 SELECT OWNER, PACKAGE_NAME, OBJECT_NAME, ARGUMENT_NAME, POSITION, SEQUENCE, DEFAULT_VALUE, DEFAULT_LENGTH, IN_OUT, DATA_LENGTH, DATA_PRECISION, DATA_SCALE, DATA_TYPE, CHAR_USED FROM SYS.ALL_ARGUMENTS WHERE (OWNER= :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) AND (PACKAGE_NAME = :PACKAGENAME OR CAST (:PACKAGENAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) AND (OBJECT_NAME = :OBJECTNAME OR CAST (:OBJECTNAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL) AND (ARGUMENT_NAME = :ARGUMENTNAME OR CAST (:ARGUMENTNAME AS VARCHAR2 (30)) IS NULL)

SELECT RTRIM (IXOWNER) AS OWNER, RTRIM (IXNAME) AS CONSTRAINT_NAME, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS SEARCH_CONDITION, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS R_OWNER, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS R_CONSTRAINT_NAME, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (9)) AS DELETE_RULE, 'ENABLED' AS STATUS, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (14)) AS DEFERRABLE, 'VALIDATED' AS VALIDATED, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (14)) AS GENERATED, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (3)) AS BAD, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (4)) AS RELY, CAST (NULL AS DATE) AS LAST_CHANGE, RTRIM (IXOWNER) AS INDEX_OWNER, RTRIM (IXNAME) AS INDEX_NAME FROM SYS.INDEXES INDEXES, SYS.TABLES TABLES WHERE INDEXES.TBLID = TABLES.TBLID AND ISUNIQUE = 0x01 AND (TBLOWNER = :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS CHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (TBLNAME = :TABLENAME OR CAST (:TABLENAME AS CHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (IXNAME = :CONSTRAINTNAME OR CAST (:CONSTRAINTNAME AS CHAR (31)) IS NULL)

SELECT RTRIM (IXOWNER) AS OWNER, RTRIM (IXNAME) AS CONSTRAINT_NAME, RTRIM (TBLNAME) AS TABLE_NAME, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS SEARCH_CONDITION, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS R_OWNER, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (30)) AS R_CONSTRAINT_NAME, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (9)) AS DELETE_RULE, 'ENABLED' AS STATUS, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (14)) AS DEFERRABLE, 'VALIDATED' AS VALIDATED, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (14)) AS GENERATED, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (3)) AS BAD, CAST (NULL AS VARCHAR2 (4)) AS RELY, CAST (NULL AS DATE) AS LAST_CHANGE, RTRIM (IXOWNER) AS INDEX_OWNER, RTRIM (IXNAME) AS INDEX_NAME FROM SYS.INDEXES INDEXES, SYS.TABLES TABLES WHERE INDEXES.TBLID = TABLES.TBLID AND ISPRIMARY = 0x01 AND (TBLOWNER = :OWNER OR CAST (:OWNER AS CHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (TBLNAME = :TABLENAME OR CAST (:TABLENAME AS CHAR (31)) IS NULL) AND (IXNAME = :CONSTRAINTNAME OR CAST (:CONSTRAINTNAME AS CHAR (31)) IS NULL)
